    <fr:title text="Being n-truncated is a proposition › "><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001P.xml" title="Being n-truncated is a proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001P" type="local">Being <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001G.xml" title="n-truncated type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link></fr:link> › </fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
  <html:p>We proceed by induction on the <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001F.xml" title="Indexing of truncation levels" addr="forest://erct/erct-001F" type="local">truncation level</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
  <html:ol><html:li>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-2]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001N.xml" title="Being contractible is a proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001N" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-001N" /></fr:link> that being <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</html:li>
    <html:li>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-1]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001O.xml" title="Being a proposition is a proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001O" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-001O" /></fr:link> that
      being a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</html:li>
    <html:li>For <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n \geq  0]]></fr:tex>, we assume by induction that being <html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n-1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> to prove that being <html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. In other words, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathsf {isTruncated}\,
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen n-1\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\,A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. By our inductive hypothesis, this is a dependent product of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link> (<fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001B.xml" title="Dependent product of propositions" addr="forest://erct/erct-001B" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-001B" /></fr:link>).</html:li></html:ol>
</fr:mainmatter>
