   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001N/0</fr:addr><fr:route>https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001N/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <html:p>Suppose we have two centres of contraction <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a,a':A]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _\bullet \colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
