 \sim  \chi '_\bullet ]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z\colon  A]]></fr:tex>, we compute:</html:p>

  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
    \begin {aligned}
      
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \chi _{a'}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
_*^{\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
